Sorcerer - ()
- Each night, may choose to either disguise someone as a different role or protect someone.
- Disguise lasts until the Sorcerer dies. Can only perform one of their abilities during the night.
- The disguise has a cooldown of 2 phases, protection does not have any cooldown. The protection is end phase and weak, while the disguise is immediate. Both abilities can only be performed during the night.
- Does not respawn.
